packets.name: THE RED MCFLY HOVER BOARD
packets.author: anonymous
packets.description: Guerrilla Music presents the new VOXEL HOVER BOARD SERIES. This limited debut from this hover board series is called "THE RED MCFLY". The meaning behind the name is attached to the film BACK 2 THE FUTURE where the main character Mart McFly is travelling on a hover board while wearing his Red vest
